00061 /** 
00062  * Constructor for creating a probe from a vector of words. 
00063  * @param vec - vector of strings containing probe information.
00064  */
00065 Probe::Probe(const std::vector<std::string> &vec, unsigned int offSet) {
00066   if(vec.size() - offSet < numFields()) {
00067     Err::errAbort("Wrong number of fields to initialize Probe. Expecting: " +
00068                     ToStr( numFields() ) + " Got: " +
00069                     ToStr( vec.size() ));
00070   }
00071   id = Convert::toInt(vec[offSet++]);
00072   type = typeForString(vec[offSet++].c_str());
00073   gcCount = (unsigned char)Convert::toInt(vec[offSet++]);
00074   offSet+=2; // ignoring length and interrogation
00075   //  seq = string(vec[offSet++]);
00076   m_apid = -1;
00077 }

00096 const char *Probe::stringForType(Probe::ProbeType t) {
00097     switch(t)
00098       {
00099       case PMST :
00100         return "pm:st";
00101       case MMST :
00102         return "mm:st";
00103       case PMAT :
00104         return "pm:at";
00105       case MMAT :
00106         return "mm:at";
00107       case GENERICAT :
00108         return "generic:at";
00109       case GENERICST :
00110         return "generic:st";
00111       case JUMBOAT :
00112         return "jumbo-checkerboard:at";
00113       case JUMBOST :
00114         return "jumbo-checkerboard:st";
00115       case THERMOAT :
00116         return "thermo:at";
00117       case THERMOST :
00118         return "thermo:st";
00119       case TRIGRIDAT :
00120         return "trigrid:at";
00121       case TRIGRIDST :
00122         return "trigrid:st";
00123       case BLANK :
00124         return "blank";
00125       default:
00126         Err::errAbort("Don't recognize Probe::pType: " + ToStr(t));
00127       }
00128     return NULL;
00129   }

00131 Probe::ProbeType Probe::typeForString(const std::string& cs) {
00132   // @todo order these by expected frequency.
00133   if (cs=="pm:st") {
00134     return PMST;
00135   }
00136   if (cs=="mm:st") {
00137     return MMST;
00138   }
00139   if ((cs=="pm:at") || (cs=="pm:target->at")) {
00140     return PMAT;
00141   }
00142   if ((cs=="mm:at") || (cs=="mm:target->at")) {
00143     return MMAT;
00144   }
00145   if ((cs=="generic:at") || (cs=="generic:target->at")) {
00146     return GENERICAT;
00147   }
00148   if ((cs=="generic:st") || (cs=="generic:target->st")) {
00149     return GENERICST;
00150   }
00151   if ((cs=="jumbo-checkerboard:at") || (cs=="edge:target->at")) {
00152     return JUMBOAT;
00153   }
00154   if ((cs=="jumbo-checkerboard:st") || (cs=="edge:target->st")) {
00155     return JUMBOST;
00156   }
00157   if ((cs=="thermo:at") || (cs=="thermo:target->at")) {
00158     return THERMOAT;
00159   }
00160   if ((cs=="thermo:st") || (cs=="thermo:target->st")) {
00161     return THERMOST;
00162   }
00163   if ((cs=="trigrid:at") || (cs=="ngrid:target->at")) {
00164     return TRIGRIDAT;
00165   }
00166   if ((cs=="trigrid:st") || (cs=="ngrid:target->st")) {
00167     return TRIGRIDST;
00168   }
00169   if ((cs=="blank") || (cs=="bar:target->st") || (cs=="bar:target->at")) {
00170     return BLANK;
00171   }
00172   //
00173   APT_ERR_ABORT("Cant convert ' "+cs+"' to Probe::ProbeType.");
00174   // return something for the compiler.
00175   return BLANK;
00176 }
